<ab facs="#facs_134_r3l29">entrunnen ſeẏ / des erb Jr euch vntervvunden habt / Darümb <expan>ſende<ex>n</ex></expan> vvir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_134_r3l30">cʒu <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> <expan>C<ex>onrad</ex></expan> <expan>Svvarcʒenberg<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan> mit ew dauon </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_134_r3l31">cʒureden vnd <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / vvaʒ <expan>derſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>dyen<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>dar<ex>ümb</ex></expan> etc ut in <expan>for<ex>ma</ex></expan> </ab>
